{"tid":407154,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎放低你最鐘意既推理小說","createTime":"2017-09-20T08:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T09:34:47.000Z","uid":22898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3ad8f222530bd013dba96c5b4ce65bfdfb9e6d","tid":407154,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"小弟睇書唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要都係東叔既書，當初係佢既《放學後》提起左我睇書既興趣。<br />\n不過佢咁多本入面最鐘意就加賀恭一郎系列，唔計早期偏本格既風格，後期既作品好多都講人性親情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢本《紅手指》睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他作家既 松本清張既 《點與線》，凑佳苗既作品都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴絲你地最鐘意既推理小書係邊本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 討論下 ，不過盡量唔好爆謎底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd6bff20f791b53ec3ffbda30d78cc87b90649e","tid":407154,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"金田一小說版"},{"pid":"93a08013d8167f19e98c4d4e6a07e4064ac0a893","tid":407154,"uid":36738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"米澤穗信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好鐘意佢有唔同風格，要青春有古典部，要黑暗有羊群宴會等等"},{"pid":"9d70b1ae9b7945b6a4c8ae25ad151c146a3425e9","tid":407154,"uid":111955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"火車"}]}